graph TD
    A[User Input\nHinglish/English] --> B[Conversational Interface\nClaude API NLP]
    B --> C[Profile Builder\nPydantic Validation + Unit Normalization]
    C --> D[Rule Engine\nDeterministic Evaluation\nPASS/FAIL/AMBIGUOUS/MISSING]
    E[(Scheme Knowledge Base\n20 JSON Rule Files)] --> D
    F[(Ambiguity Map\n10+ Annotations)] --> D
    D --> G[Confidence Scorer\nWeighted Aggregation\nsum_passed + 0.5×sum_ambiguous / sum_evaluated]
    G --> H[Gap Analyzer\nMISSING_INPUT\nAMBIGUOUS_CRITERION\nMISSING_PREREQUISITE]
    G --> I[Doc Checklist Generator\nPrioritised by processing time]
    G --> J[Prerequisite Sequencer\nTopological sort via networkx]
    H --> K[Output Formatter\nrich tables + panels]
    I --> K
    J --> K
    K --> L[Results\nELIGIBLE / LIKELY / AMBIGUOUS / INELIGIBLE\nwith full explainability]
